## Install Puppet : 


in this lab we are going to install and configure puppet ecosystem using 3 Redhat9 VMS.
Prerequisites : 
1 Vm for puppet-master 
2 Vms for puppet-agents
Use NAT as a network process to let Vms acces the internet. 
power On those Vms.
We will change hostname :
- Puppet Server 
hostnamectl set-hostname puppetmaster
vi /etc/hosts
